OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWhy is Russia making claims
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fabout a 'dirty bomb'?      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Russia's defence minister has claimed  
OL,6, Ukraine might use a "dirty bomb" - a   
OL,7, device containing radioactive material 
OL,8, as well as conventional explosives.    
OL,10,FHe has not offered any evidence, and   
OL,11,FUkraine - as well as France, the UK and
OL,12,Fthe US - has dismissed the allegations.
OL,14,FSergei Shoigu told the UK's defence    
OL,15,Fsecretary, Ben Wallace, that he was    
OL,16,F"concerned about possible provocations 
OL,17,Fby Kyiv involving the use of a dirty   
OL,18,Fbomb".                                 
